<PAGE width="419.64" height="595.32" number="233" id="p233"><MEDIABOX x1="0" y1="0" x2="419.64" y2="595.32"/><CROPBOX x1="0" y1="0" x2="419.64" y2="595.32"/><BLEEDBOX x1="0" y1="0" x2="419.64" y2="595.32"/><ARTBOX x1="0" y1="0" x2="419.64" y2="595.32"/><TRIMBOX x1="0" y1="0" x2="419.64" y2="595.32"/><TEXT width="12.7715" height="7.668" id="p233_t1" x="203.45" y="569.101"><TOKEN sid="p233_s22862" id="p233_w1" font-name="Times New Roman" symbolic="yes" serif="yes" fixed-width="yes" bold="no" italic="no" font-size="8.52" font-color="#000000" rotation="0" angle="0" x="203.45" y="569.101" base="574.92" width="12.7715" height="7.668">233</TOKEN></TEXT><TEXT width="228.969" height="9" id="p233_t2" x="48.264" y="46.08"><TOKEN sid="p233_s22864" id="p233_w2" font-name="IPA¾©" serif="yes" bold="no" italic="no" font-size="9" font-color="#000000" rotation="0" angle="0" x="48.264" y="46.08" base="54" width="228.969" height="9">現金で特急のゴイットを購入する。席が空いていて助かった。</TOKEN></TEXT><TEXT width="319.885" height="9" id="p233_t3" x="56.424" y="63.02"><TOKEN sid="p233_s22867" id="p233_w3" font-name="ipa¾©" serif="yes" bold="no" italic="no" font-size="9" font-color="#000000" rotation="0" angle="0" x="56.424" y="63.02" base="70.94" width="170.507" height="9">私たちはゕンギの電源を切ることにした。GPS</TOKEN><TOKEN sid="p233_s22868" id="p233_w4" font-name="ipa¾©" serif="yes" bold="no" italic="no" font-size="9" font-color="#000000" rotation="0" angle="0" x="228.43" y="63.02" base="70.94" width="147.879" height="9">で居場所を突き止められる恐れがある。</TOKEN></TEXT><TEXT width="277.812" height="9" id="p233_t4" x="56.424" y="80.06"><TOKEN sid="p233_s22871" id="p233_w5" font-name="ipa¾©" serif="yes" bold="no" italic="no" font-size="9" font-color="#000000" rotation="0" angle="0" x="56.424" y="80.06" base="87.98" width="277.812" height="9">昨日はほとんど眠れなかったので、私たちは電車の中で泥のように眠った。</TOKEN></TEXT><TEXT width="315.966" height="9" id="p233_t5" x="56.424" y="97.1"><TOKEN sid="p233_s22874" id="p233_w6" font-name="ipa¾©" serif="yes" bold="no" italic="no" font-size="9" font-color="#000000" rotation="0" angle="0" x="56.424" y="97.1" base="105.02" width="315.966" height="9">途中で目が醒めると、いつの間にか上着が毛布代わりにかけられていた。ゕルオ゚さん</TOKEN></TEXT><TEXT width="17.16" height="9" id="p233_t6" x="48.264" y="114.02"><TOKEN sid="p233_s22875" id="p233_w7" font-name="ipa¾©" serif="yes" bold="no" italic="no" font-size="9" font-color="#000000" rotation="0" angle="0" x="48.264" y="114.02" base="121.94" width="17.16" height="9">だ。</TOKEN></TEXT><TEXT width="310.516" height="9" id="p233_t7" x="56.424" y="131.06"><TOKEN sid="p233_s22878" id="p233_w8" font-name="ipa¾©" serif="yes" bold="no" italic="no" font-size="9" font-color="#000000" rotation="0" angle="0" x="56.424" y="131.06" base="138.98" width="310.516" height="9">どこまでも優しいなぁ……。あ、この上着、ゕルオ゚さんの匂いがする。えへ……。</TOKEN></TEXT><TEXT width="172.686" height="10.035" id="p233_t8" x="56.544" y="147.875"><TOKEN sid="p233_s22881" id="p233_w9" font-name="Arial" symbolic="yes" fixed-width="yes" bold="no" italic="no" font-size="9" font-color="#000000" rotation="0" angle="0" x="56.544" y="147.875" base="156.02" width="172.686" height="10.035">――と思った瞬間、背筋がぞくぞくっとした。</TOKEN></TEXT><TEXT width="316.156" height="9" id="p233_t9" x="56.424" y="165.05"><TOKEN sid="p233_s22884" id="p233_w10" font-name="ipa¾©" serif="yes" bold="no" italic="no" font-size="9" font-color="#000000" rotation="0" angle="0" x="56.424" y="165.05" base="172.97" width="162.639" height="9">うっわ、今あんた何て言ったよ、初月紫苑！</TOKEN><TOKEN sid="p233_s22885" id="p233_w11" font-name="ipa¾©" serif="yes" bold="no" italic="no" font-size="9" font-color="#000000" rotation="0" angle="0" x="225.65" y="165.05" base="172.97" width="106.11" height="9">「えへ」とか言っちゃった？</TOKEN><TOKEN sid="p233_s22886" id="p233_w12" font-name="ipa¾©" serif="yes" bold="no" italic="no" font-size="9" font-color="#000000" rotation="0" angle="0" x="339.1" y="165.05" base="172.97" width="33.48" height="9">それ言っ</TOKEN></TEXT><TEXT width="220.926" height="9" id="p233_t10" x="48.264" y="182.09"><TOKEN sid="p233_s22887" id="p233_w13" font-name="ipa¾©" serif="yes" bold="no" italic="no" font-size="9" font-color="#000000" rotation="0" angle="0" x="48.264" y="182.09" base="190.01" width="220.926" height="9">ていいのは幼女とレ゗ンと二次元だけだって法律知ってる？</TOKEN></TEXT><TEXT width="315.975" height="9" id="p233_t11" x="56.424" y="199.13"><TOKEN sid="p233_s22890" id="p233_w14" font-name="ipa¾©" serif="yes" bold="no" italic="no" font-size="9" font-color="#000000" rotation="0" angle="0" x="56.424" y="199.13" base="207.05" width="315.975" height="9">激しい自己嫌悪に苛まれながらも、上着の匂いをこそこそ嗅いではやっぱり「えへ」と</TOKEN></TEXT><TEXT width="57.96" height="9" id="p233_t12" x="48.264" y="216.05"><TOKEN sid="p233_s22891" id="p233_w15" font-name="ipa¾©" serif="yes" bold="no" italic="no" font-size="9" font-color="#000000" rotation="0" angle="0" x="48.264" y="216.05" base="223.97" width="57.96" height="9">か言ってみた。</TOKEN></TEXT><TEXT width="316.153" height="9" id="p233_t13" x="56.424" y="250.13"><TOKEN sid="p233_s22895" id="p233_w16" font-name="ipa¾©" serif="yes" bold="no" italic="no" font-size="9" font-color="#000000" rotation="0" angle="0" x="56.424" y="250.13" base="258.05" width="316.153" height="9">ゕルオゕ市に着いたときは既に夕方になっていた。特急を使ったわりにはずいぶん時間</TOKEN></TEXT><TEXT width="324.126" height="9" id="p233_t14" x="48.264" y="267.05"><TOKEN sid="p233_s22896" id="p233_w17" font-name="ipa¾©" serif="yes" bold="no" italic="no" font-size="9" font-color="#000000" rotation="0" angle="0" x="48.264" y="267.05" base="274.97" width="324.126" height="9">がかかってしまった。脚と腰が長時間の乗車で悲鳴を上げている。ゕルバォードは思った</TOKEN></TEXT><TEXT width="57.96" height="9" id="p233_t15" x="48.264" y="284.11"><TOKEN sid="p233_s22897" id="p233_w18" font-name="ipa¾©" serif="yes" bold="no" italic="no" font-size="9" font-color="#000000" rotation="0" angle="0" x="48.264" y="284.11" base="292.03" width="57.96" height="9">より広い国だ。</TOKEN></TEXT><TEXT width="41.64" height="9" id="p233_t16" x="56.424" y="301.15"><TOKEN sid="p233_s22900" id="p233_w19" font-name="ipa¾©" serif="yes" bold="no" italic="no" font-size="9" font-color="#000000" rotation="0" angle="0" x="56.424" y="301.15" base="309.07" width="41.64" height="9">駅を出る。</TOKEN></TEXT><TEXT width="314.566" height="9.873" id="p233_t17" x="56.424" y="318.07"><TOKEN sid="p233_s22903" id="p233_w20" font-name="ipa¾©" serif="yes" bold="no" italic="no" font-size="9" font-color="#000000" rotation="0" angle="0" x="56.424" y="318.07" base="325.99" width="245.172" height="9">ここから隠れ家まではかなりの距離がある。レ゗ンの話だと車でも</TOKEN><TOKEN sid="p233_s22904" id="p233_w21" font-name="times new roman" symbolic="yes" serif="yes" fixed-width="yes" bold="no" italic="no" font-size="9" font-color="#000000" rotation="0" angle="0" x="302.95" y="319.843" base="325.99" width="8.58" height="8.1">30</TOKEN><TOKEN sid="p233_s22905" id="p233_w22" font-name="ipa¾©" serif="yes" bold="no" italic="no" font-size="9" font-color="#000000" rotation="0" angle="0" x="313.03" y="318.07" base="325.99" width="57.96" height="9">分はかかるとい</TOKEN></TEXT><TEXT width="17.16" height="9" id="p233_t18" x="48.264" y="335.11"><TOKEN sid="p233_s22906" id="p233_w23" font-name="ipa¾©" serif="yes" bold="no" italic="no" font-size="9" font-color="#000000" rotation="0" angle="0" x="48.264" y="335.11" base="343.03" width="17.16" height="9">う。</TOKEN></TEXT><TEXT width="315.598" height="9.873" id="p233_t19" x="56.424" y="352.15"><TOKEN sid="p233_s22909" id="p233_w24" font-name="ipa¾©" serif="yes" bold="no" italic="no" font-size="9" font-color="#000000" rotation="0" angle="0" x="56.424" y="352.15" base="360.07" width="210.966" height="9">歩くとなるとどれくらいかかるのだろう。車で郊外を時速</TOKEN><TOKEN sid="p233_s22910" id="p233_w25" font-name="times new roman" symbolic="yes" serif="yes" fixed-width="yes" bold="no" italic="no" font-size="9" font-color="#000000" rotation="0" angle="0" x="268.63" y="353.923" base="360.07" width="19.242" height="8.1">60km</TOKEN><TOKEN sid="p233_s22911" id="p233_w26" font-name="ipa¾©" serif="yes" bold="no" italic="no" font-size="9" font-color="#000000" rotation="0" angle="0" x="289.27" y="352.15" base="360.07" width="82.752" height="9">で走ったとして、30km</TOKEN></TEXT><TEXT width="296.686" height="9.873" id="p233_t20" x="48.264" y="369.07"><TOKEN sid="p233_s22912" id="p233_w27" font-name="ipa¾©" serif="yes" bold="no" italic="no" font-size="9" font-color="#000000" rotation="0" angle="0" x="48.264" y="369.07" base="376.99" width="147.486" height="9">くらいか。歩いていくには厳しい。時速</TOKEN><TOKEN sid="p233_s22913" id="p233_w28" font-name="times new roman" symbolic="yes" serif="yes" fixed-width="yes" bold="no" italic="no" font-size="9" font-color="#000000" rotation="0" angle="0" x="197.09" y="370.843" base="376.99" width="15.162" height="8.1">5km</TOKEN><TOKEN sid="p233_s22914" id="p233_w29" font-name="ipa¾©" serif="yes" bold="no" italic="no" font-size="9" font-color="#000000" rotation="0" angle="0" x="213.65" y="369.07" base="376.99" width="66.12" height="9">で歩いたとしても</TOKEN><TOKEN sid="p233_s22915" id="p233_w30" font-name="times new roman" symbolic="yes" serif="yes" fixed-width="yes" bold="no" italic="no" font-size="9" font-color="#000000" rotation="0" angle="0" x="280.99" y="370.843" base="376.99" width="4.5" height="8.1">6</TOKEN><TOKEN sid="p233_s22916" id="p233_w31" font-name="ipa¾©" serif="yes" bold="no" italic="no" font-size="9" font-color="#000000" rotation="0" angle="0" x="286.99" y="369.07" base="376.99" width="57.96" height="9">時間はかかる。</TOKEN></TEXT><TEXT width="155.657" height="9" id="p233_t21" x="56.424" y="386.11"><TOKEN sid="p233_s22919" id="p233_w32" font-name="ipa¾©" serif="yes" bold="no" italic="no" font-size="9" font-color="#000000" rotation="0" angle="0" x="56.424" y="386.11" base="394.03" width="155.657" height="9">まいったな……徒歩じゃとても無理だわ。</TOKEN></TEXT><TEXT width="319.996" height="9.873" id="p233_t22" x="56.424" y="420.1"><TOKEN sid="p233_s22923" id="p233_w33" font-name="ipa¾©" serif="yes" bold="no" italic="no" font-size="9" font-color="#000000" rotation="0" angle="0" x="56.424" y="420.1" base="428.02" width="245.397" height="9">私が頭を抱えていると、ちょうど日本でいう高校生くらいの少女が</TOKEN><TOKEN sid="p233_s22924" id="p233_w34" font-name="times new roman" symbolic="yes" serif="yes" fixed-width="yes" bold="no" italic="no" font-size="9" font-color="#000000" rotation="0" angle="0" x="303.31" y="421.873" base="428.02" width="4.5" height="8.1">3</TOKEN><TOKEN sid="p233_s22925" id="p233_w35" font-name="ipa¾©" serif="yes" bold="no" italic="no" font-size="9" font-color="#000000" rotation="0" angle="0" x="309.43" y="420.1" base="428.02" width="66.99" height="9">人通りかかった。</TOKEN></TEXT><TEXT width="245.289" height="9" id="p233_t23" x="48.264" y="437.14"><TOKEN sid="p233_s22926" id="p233_w36" font-name="ipa¾©" serif="yes" bold="no" italic="no" font-size="9" font-color="#000000" rotation="0" angle="0" x="48.264" y="437.14" base="445.06" width="245.289" height="9">そして一時的に自転車を道に停め、駅近くの売店に入っていった。</TOKEN></TEXT><TEXT width="21.771" height="10.125" id="p233_t24" x="48.264" y="454.132"><TOKEN sid="p233_s22928" id="p233_w37" href="http://mindsc.ape.jp/klel/yui.cgi?xik=enxik&amp;axn=axnyui&amp;ism=ismyui&amp;rein=mm&amp;ziko=ilm" font-name="kardinal" symbolic="yes" fixed-width="yes" bold="no" italic="no" font-size="9" font-color="#000000" rotation="0" angle="0" x="48.264" y="454.132" base="461.62" width="21.771" height="10.125">"mm..."</TOKEN></TEXT><TEXT width="163.806" height="9" id="p233_t25" x="56.424" y="471.1"><TOKEN sid="p233_s22931" id="p233_w38" font-name="ipa¾©" serif="yes" bold="no" italic="no" font-size="9" font-color="#000000" rotation="0" angle="0" x="56.424" y="471.1" base="479.02" width="163.806" height="9">これは使えそうだという顔のゕルオ゚さん。</TOKEN></TEXT><TEXT width="188.286" height="9" id="p233_t26" x="56.424" y="488.136"><TOKEN sid="p233_s22934" id="p233_w39" font-name="ipa¾©" serif="yes" bold="no" italic="no" font-size="9" font-color="#000000" rotation="0" angle="0" x="56.424" y="488.136" base="496.056" width="188.286" height="9">レ゗ンは困った顔で彼の袖をくいくいと引っ張る。</TOKEN></TEXT><TEXT width="45.648" height="10.125" id="p233_t27" x="48.264" y="505.152"><TOKEN sid="p233_s22936" id="p233_w40" href="http://mindsc.ape.jp/klel/yui.cgi?xik=enxik&amp;axn=axnyui&amp;ism=ismyui&amp;rein=wein&amp;ziko=ilm" font-name="kardinal" symbolic="yes" fixed-width="yes" bold="no" italic="no" font-size="9" font-color="#000000" rotation="0" angle="0" x="48.264" y="505.152" base="512.64" width="24.243" height="10.125">"wein,</TOKEN><TOKEN sid="p233_s22937" id="p233_w41" href="http://mindsc.ape.jp/klel/yui.cgi?xik=enxik&amp;axn=axnyui&amp;ism=ismyui&amp;rein=arxe&amp;ziko=ilm" font-name="kardinal" symbolic="yes" fixed-width="yes" bold="no" italic="no" font-size="9" font-color="#000000" rotation="0" angle="0" x="76.224" y="505.152" base="512.64" width="17.688" height="10.125">arxe"</TOKEN></TEXT><TEXT width="64.844" height="10.125" id="p233_t28" x="48.264" y="522.072"><TOKEN sid="p233_s22939" id="p233_w42" href="http://mindsc.ape.jp/klel/yui.cgi?xik=enxik&amp;axn=axnyui&amp;ism=ismyui&amp;rein=tal&amp;ziko=ilm" font-name="kardinal" symbolic="yes" fixed-width="yes" bold="no" italic="no" font-size="9" font-color="#000000" rotation="0" angle="0" x="48.264" y="522.072" base="529.56" width="9.141" height="10.125">"tal</TOKEN><TOKEN sid="p233_s22940" id="p233_w43" href="http://mindsc.ape.jp/klel/yui.cgi?xik=enxik&amp;axn=axnyui&amp;ism=ismyui&amp;rein=tu&amp;ziko=ilm" font-name="kardinal" symbolic="yes" fixed-width="yes" bold="no" italic="no" font-size="9" font-color="#000000" rotation="0" angle="0" x="60.984" y="522.072" base="529.56" width="7.197" height="10.125">tu</TOKEN><TOKEN sid="p233_s22941" id="p233_w44" href="http://mindsc.ape.jp/klel/yui.cgi?xik=enxik&amp;axn=axnyui&amp;ism=ismyui&amp;rein=et&amp;ziko=ilm" font-name="kardinal" symbolic="yes" fixed-width="yes" bold="no" italic="no" font-size="9" font-color="#000000" rotation="0" angle="0" x="71.784" y="522.072" base="529.56" width="7.056" height="10.125">et</TOKEN><TOKEN sid="p233_s22942" id="p233_w45" href="http://mindsc.ape.jp/klel/yui.cgi?xik=enxik&amp;axn=axnyui&amp;ism=ismyui&amp;rein=vilfonl&amp;ziko=ilm" font-name="kardinal" symbolic="yes" fixed-width="yes" bold="no" italic="no" font-size="9" font-color="#000000" rotation="0" angle="0" x="82.584" y="522.072" base="529.56" width="30.524" height="10.125">vilfonl"</TOKEN></TEXT><TEXT width="38.808" height="10.125" id="p233_t29" x="48.264" y="539.112"><TOKEN sid="p233_s22944" id="p233_w46" href="http://mindsc.ape.jp/klel/yui.cgi?xik=enxik&amp;axn=axnyui&amp;ism=ismyui&amp;rein=senfonl&amp;ziko=ilm" font-name="kardinal" symbolic="yes" fixed-width="yes" bold="no" italic="no" font-size="9" font-color="#000000" rotation="0" angle="0" x="48.264" y="539.112" base="546.6" width="38.808" height="10.125">"senfonl!"</TOKEN></TEXT></PAGE>
